        As the UK <strong>emerges from lockdown</strong>, work has begun to rebuild our battered economy in a way that saves and creates jobs, that empowers innovation and that incorporates the resilience necessary to cope with future threats. The <strong>engineering community</strong> will play an important role in this <strong>post-pandemic world</strong>.</p><p>Watch our distinguished panel map out the future of one of our most important industries.
